The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 BCCI butts into DD breaks

Chandigarh: Commercial breaks at important junctures of cricket matches is one aspect that Doordarshan viewers have long been complaining about. 

Acting in viewers interest, the BCCI has decided to talk to the national broadcaster over the issue so that fans do not miss out on seeing crucial moments of the match. 




